---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About AGrowth" description="Learn about Ad Account Desk by AGrowth and its focus on advertising account restrictions, compliance, appeals and operations.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">About AGrowth</p>
      <h1>Practical knowledge for complex ad account operations.</h1>
      <p class="lede">Ad Account Desk by AGrowth organizes common advertising account issues into clear platform, compliance, appeal, and operational focus areas.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section section--white">
    <div class="container info-layout">
      <div class="info-aside">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our focus</p>
        <p>Meta Ads · Google Ads · TikTok Ads · Appeals · Compliance · Agency accounts</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Built to make the next step clearer.</h2>
        <p>Advertising account restrictions can involve platform policy, billing, identity, business verification, security, or connected assets. The Desk brings those areas together so operators can diagnose issues more methodically.</p>
        <p>Our coverage spans Facebook and Meta ad account restrictions, Google Ads suspensions, TikTok Ads and Business Center enforcement, appeal preparation, agency account options, and cross-platform account operations.</p>
        <h3>Independent guidance</h3>
        <p>AGrowth is not Meta, Google, or TikTok, and does not control their enforcement decisions. Platform names and trademarks belong to their respective owners.</p>
        <h3>Responsible operations</h3>
        <p>Our editorial approach favors accurate business information, documented access, secure payment operations, transparent provider relationships, and compliance with applicable platform policies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
